ng\"></li>\n        </ul>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p></p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11\">\n    <h4><span>燎</span>字的基本解释</h4>\n    <div>\n      <p>燎<br>liáo<br>延烧：燎荒。燎原烈火。<br>烫：燎泡。<br>照明。<br><br>燎<br>liǎo<br>挨近火而烧焦：把头发燎了。<br><br></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>燎</span>字的汉语字典释义</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>[①]［liǎo］<br>［《廣韻》力小切，上小，來。］<br>［《廣韻》力照切，去笑，來。］<br>“轑4”的被通假字。<br>(1)放火烧田中杂草。<br>(2)泛指延烧；烧。<br>(3)烘烤。<br>(4)被火焰烧焦。<br>(5)用同“憭”。明白，明了。<br>[②]［liáo］<br>［《廣韻》力昭切，平宵，來。］<br>(1)火炬。<br>(2)烫。参见“燎2泡”、“燎2漿”。<br>[③]［liào］<br>［《廣韻》力照切，去笑，來。］<br>(1)照明。<br>(2)古祭名。烧柴祭天。古作“尞”。<br>(3)指柴薪。<br>(4)夜猎。参见“燎3獵”。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>燎</span>字的英文翻译</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>◎ <b>燎</b><br>burn</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>燎</span>字的康熙字典解释</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>【巳集中】【火字部】　燎； 康熙笔画：16； 页码：<a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/kangxi/0683.gif\" target=\"_blank\"><span>页683第02</span></a><br>【玉篇】【正韻】?力弔切，音料。【玉篇】庭燎國之大事，樹以照衆也。【詩·小雅】庭燎之光。【釋文】鄭云：在地曰燎，執之曰燭，樹之門外曰大燭，於內曰庭燎，皆是照衆爲明。【禮·月令】以共郊廟及百祀之薪燎。【周禮·天官·閽人】設門燎。【註】地燭也。　又【玉篇】放火也。　又【詩·陳風】佼人燎兮。【朱傳】燎明也。　又【詩·小雅】燎之方揚。【箋】火田曰燎。　又【廣韻】【集韻】【韻會】【正韻】?力照切，音療。【廣韻】照也。　又【廣韻】一曰宵田。　又【廣韻】放火也。【詩·大雅】瑟彼柞棫，民所燎矣。又【集韻】本作尞。【前漢·郊祀志】尞禋有常用。【註】師古曰：尞與燎同。　又【唐韻】力小切【集韻】【韻會】朗鳥切【正韻】盧絞切，?音繚。【說文】本作?，亦放火也。【書·盤庚】若火之燎于原。【註】燎，力召反。又力鳥反。　又【集韻】或作?。亦作轑。【前漢·杜欽傳】欲以熏轑天下。【註】師古曰：轑，讀曰燎。假借用字。　又【集韻】憐蕭切，音聊。縱火焚也。　又離昭切，音摎。火在地曰燎。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>燎</span>字的源字形</div>\n    <div>\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>燎</span>字的起名意思</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>：常指放火烧草木或火延烧原野。又喻火烧气势旺盛，着火面积大。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_en_transl\">burn<br>Basic explanation of words<br>burn<br>liáo<br>Burning: Burning a desolation. Start a prairie fire.<br>Hot: Singe.<br>illumination.<br>burn<br>liǎo<br>Scorched by the fire: scorched hair.<br>burn<br>Chinese dictionary definition of words<br>[①]［liǎo］<br>[\"Guangyun\" is a little cut, come on, come on. ]<br>[\"Guangyun\" try to cut, laugh, come. ]<br>The false character of \"轑4\" was passed.<br>(1) Set fire to weeds in the field.<br>(2) Broadly refers to extended burning; burning.<br>(3) Baking.<br>(4) Scorched by flames.<br>(5) Use the same as \"Xin\". Understand, understand.<br>[②]［liáo］<br>[\"Guangyun\" forcefully cut, and at night, come. ]<br>(1) Torch.<br>(2) Hot. See \"Liao 2 Bubbles\", \"Liao 2 Pulp\".<br>[③]［liào］<br>[\"Guangyun\" try to cut, laugh, come. ]<br>(1) Lighting.<br>(2) The name of the ancient festival. Burn wood to worship the sky. The ancient work \"尞\".<br>(3) Refers to firewood.<br>(4) Night hunting. See \"Liao 3 Hunting\".<br>burn<br>English translation of words<br>◎ Singe<br>burn<br>burn<br>Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words<br>[Si Collection] [Fire Word Department] 　燎; Kangxi strokes: 16; Page number: page 683 02<br>[Jade articles] [Positive rhyme]? Force hanging and cutting, sound material. [Jade articles] Ting Liao country's major events, the tree is also for the public. 【Poetry·Xiaoya】The light of Ting Liao. 【Explanation】Zheng Yun: It is called Liao in the ground, candle is called to hold it, big candle is called outside the door of the tree, and it is called Liao in the courtyard. They are all according to the public. 【Rite·Monthly Order】With the salaries of Gongjiao Temple and Baisi. 【Zhou Li·Tian Guan·Huan Ren】Set up the door and Liao. [Note] Ground candles are also.　[Jade articles] Set on fire again.　[Poetry·Chen Feng] The outstanding person Liao Xi. 【Zhu Chuan】Liaoming also.　[Poetry·Xiaoya] Fang Yang of Liaozhi. [Note] Huo Tian said singe.　 [Guang Yun] [Ji Yun] [Yun Hui] [Zheng Yun]? Li Zhaoqi, sound therapy. [Guang Yun] Photo also.　[Guang Yun] One day, Xiao Tian.　[Guangyun] Set on fire again. 【Poetry·Daya】Sebi 柞棫, the people are scorched. Also 【Jiyun】This is a 尞. [Pre-Han · Jiao Si Zhi] Glutton used to be commonly used. [Note] Shi Gu said: Si and Liao are the same.　 [Tang Yun] Li Xiaoqie [Ji Yun] [Yun Hui] Lang Bird Cut [Zheng Yun] Lu Jiaoqie,? Yin Liao. [Said the text] This work is also set on fire. 【Book·Pangeng】If the fire ignited in the prairie. [Note] Singe, and call for rebellion. And force the bird against.　 [Ji Yun] or Zuo?. Also used as 轑. [Previous Han · Du Qin Biography] I want to smoke the world. [Note] Shigu said: \"Ji\", \"Liao\" in reading. Falsely borrowed words.　[Jiyun] Pity and sorrow, voice chat. Arson also burned.　 Li Zhaoqie again, Yinji. The fire sings on the ground.<br>burn<br>Source glyph<br>burn<br>Name meaning<br>: Often refers to setting fire to vegetation or fire to burn the wilderness. Yu Yu was vigorous and the fire area was large.</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148274635650880.png\" target=\"_blank\"><object data=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148274635650880.png\" type=\"image/png\"><img src=\"yw11-zixing-zi148274635650880.png\"></object></a></div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_chinese\">燎<br>liáo<br>燎<br>烽<br>原作“条”。《汉书》:“雷电条,<br>获白麟”。字的上部像一些交错放<br>置的木柴,下面是火,点拔物是木<br>柴燃烧时进发出的火星。</div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_ru_transl\">гореть<br>гореть<br>Маяк<br>Оригинал «Статьи».<br>«Хань Шу»: «Статья о громе и молнии, победила Байлинь».<br>Верхняя часть персонажа похожа на какие-то шахматные дрова, нижняя часть - это огонь, а точка - это искра, которая появляется при горении дров.</div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"bkrs_pinyin\">liáo, liǎo</div>\n<div id=\"bkrs_transl\">\n  <div><strong>I</strong></div>\n  <div><span class=\"paragraph\">гл.</span> <strong>А</strong></div>\n  <div>1) гореть, пылать; полыхать, бушевать (<i>о пламени</i>)</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">若火之燎于原, 不可向迩 подобно огню, что бушует в степи, близко нельзя подойти</span></div>\n  <div>2) сгорать, превращаться в пепел</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">以之投火, 经宿不燎 если ж в огонь его бросить, он за целую ночь не сгорит!</span></div>\n  <div>3) высыхать, сохнуть (<i>на огне</i>)</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">以火自燎 совершенно высохнуть на огне</span></div>\n  <div>4) <span class=\"paragraph\">вм.</span> <span class=\"reference\">獠</span> (<i>охотиться ночью</i>)</div>\n  <div><span class=\"paragraph\">гл.</span> <strong>Б</strong></div>\n  <div>1) выжигать растительность (<i>готовя землю под пахоту</i>)</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">燎草木 выжигать траву и деревья, готовить целину</span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">燎田 выжигать землю под пахоту</span></div>\n  <div>2) <strong>liǎo</strong> опалять, сжигать; охватывать (<i>об огне</i>) ; прижигать</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">灯把胡子燎了 опалить бороду над пламенем лампы</span></div>\n  <div>3) сушить на огне</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">对灶燎衣 сушить платье перед очагом</span></div>\n  <div><strong>II </strong><i>прил. /наречие</i></div>\n  <div><span class=\"paragraph\">устар.</span> яркий, блестящий; светлый, ясный</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">佼人燎兮 о, как блестящ красавец этот!</span></div>\n  <div><strong>III</strong> <span class=\"paragraph\">сущ.</span></div>\n  <div>1) огонь, пламя; сигнальный костёр; светильник, факел (<i>особенно: на воздухе</i>)</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">庭燎 факелы (костёр) во дворе</span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">燎火 огонь сигнального костра</span></div>\n  <div>2) ожог</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">燎浆泡 волдырь от ожога</span></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mdbg.net/chinese/dictionary?page=worddict&wdrst=0&wdqtm=0&wdqcham=1&wdqt=\">MDBG</a> | <a href=\"https://bkrs.info/slovo.php?ch=燎\">BKRS</a> | <a href=\"https://dictionary.writtenchinese.com/#sk=燎&svt=pinyin\">WriCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.qianyix.com/words/index.php?q=燎\">Qianyix</a> | <a href=\"https://www.yellowbridge.com/chinese/sentsearch.php?word=燎\">YBridge</a> | <a href=\"http://cca.xingtanlu.cn/?action=page&pid=8&do=search&name=燎\">Collocs</a> | <a href=\"https://characterpop.com/explode/燎\">ChPop</a> | <a href=\"https://visualchinesesearch.com/?query=燎\">SimCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.hanzicraft.com/character/燎\">Stats</a> | <a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/search?q=燎&tbm=isch\">Google Images</a> | <a href=\"https://namakajiri.net/kanjigen/#燎\">Char lookup site</a></p>\n<div class=\"optional notes small\">亠 (крышка), 并, 大 (большой), 小 (маленький), 日 (день), 火 (огонь)</div>\n<dl class=\"optional words\">\n  <dt>燎原<rt>りょうげん</rt>\n  </dt>\n  <dd>\n    <li>степной пожар (в т.ч. организованное выжигание травы)</li>\n  </dd>\n  <dt>庭燎<rt>にわび</rt>\n  </dt>\n  <dd>\n    <li>garden bonfire (esp. one held on the imperial grounds)</li><cite>edict2</cite>\n  </dd>\n</dl>","glyphs":[{"glyph":"火","pinyins":["Huo3","huo3"]},{"glyph":"尞","pinyins":["fill"]}]}